side popout will include :
dashboard :
    weather
    warp toggle
    IP address
    network strength
Audio:
    Current audio source
    Slider for file progress
    Next, Pause and skip button
    Icon of audio source, spotify icon etc etc
    Audio Visualiser
CPU/GPU:
    CPU Temp + load
    GPU Temp + load
    RAM usage
Task manager:
    Running processes (sorted by either RAM or cpu usage)
    RAM + CPU usage

Left Top bar will include:
power button - leads to wlogout like popup
Workspace:
    Workspace ID
    Workspace Window Name
    Button to switch workspaces

Middle top bar will include:
Time popup (time is shown on popup area)
Popup includes:
    Date DD/MM/YYYY
    Day of Week
    Calendar (maybe events but that might take too much space)

Right top bar will include:
Battery popup (icon shows a slider with colour variation based on percentage, charger icon over the battery icon when plugged)
Includes:
    Performance Choice (Performance,Optimised and Saver)
    Time left on battery

Audio + Brightness popups(Audio icon will vary with loudness set):
Includes:
    Sliders for brightness and audio

Notifications appear underneath the right top bar icons (shift down when popups appear) 